name: KoinexpricesofBitcoinEthereuminIndianRupees
0:
”Alexa, Ask Koinex rupees for the price of Bitcoin”
”Alexa, launch Koinex rupees”
”How much is Ethereum worth?”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: koinex rupees
des:
The skill fetches the latest price of Bitcoins, Ethereum and many other crypto currency's prices from Koinex. 
The data fetched will always be the latest available and always in Indian Rupees.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
